<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cetak Surat Keterangan Beda Identitas</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        /* Global Styles */
        body {
            font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
    
        /* Kertas A4 yang responsif */
        .paper {
            width: 794px;
            height: 1123px;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 40px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            position: relative;
            border: none;
            margin: 20px;
        }
    
        .garis-bawah {
            border-bottom: 2px solid black;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
    
        /* Header */
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
    
        .logo {
            width: 80px;
            position: absolute;
            left: 12px;
            top: 5px;
        }
    
        .header h3 {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: normal;
        }
    
        .header h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 5px 0;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            word-spacing: 5px;
        }
    
        .header p {
            margin: 2px 0;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
    
        .header .line {
            width: 100%;
            height: 2px;
            background-color: black;
            margin-top: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
    
        .kode-desa {
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
    
        /* Judul Surat */
        .judul-surat {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
    
        .judul-surat h3 {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    
        .judul-surat p {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: -5px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
    
        /* Isi Surat */
        .content {
            margin-top: 20px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-align: left;
        }
    
        .content p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            display: block;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }
    
        .content strong {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    
        /* Improved alignment for data fields */
        .data-container {
            display: flex;
            margin-left: 38px;
        }
    
        .data-label {
            width: 220px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
    
        .data-value {
            flex-grow: 1;
        }
    
        .data-value strong {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    
        /* Special alignment for the first name field */
        .first-name-container {
            display: flex;
            margin-left: 38px;
        }
    
        .first-name-label {
            width: 220px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
    
        .first-name-value {
            flex-grow: 1;
        }
    
        /* Tanda Tangan */
        .signature-block {
            margin-top: 60px;
            font-size: 14px;
            width: 100%;
        }
    
        .signature-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            width: 100%;
        }
    
        .tanggal-ttd {
            margin-right: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }
    
        .ttd-kanan {
            text-align: center;
            width: 300px;
            margin-right: 50px;
        }
    
        .ttd-kanan p {
            margin: 3px 0;
        }
    
        .signature-name {
            text-decoration: underline;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 80px;
        }
    
        .signature-line {
            width: 200px;
            height: 1px;
            border-top: 1px solid black;
            margin: 0 auto;
            position: relative;
            top: -20px;
        }
    
        /* Tombol */
        .no-print button {
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin: 0 10px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
    
        .btn-print {
            background-color: #28a745;
            color: white;
        }
    
        .btn-back {
            background-color: #6c757d;
            color: white;
        }
    
        .no-print button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }
    
        .no-print button:active {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    
        /* Hanya untuk tampilan di browser */
        @media screen {
            .no-print {
                display: block;
                text-align: center;
                margin-top: 20px;
            }
        }
    
        /* Tidak muncul di PDF */
        @media print {
            @page {
                size: A4;
                margin-top: 2cm;
                margin-bottom: 2cm;
                margin-left: 2.5cm;
                margin-right: 2cm;
            }
    
            body {
                margin: 0 !important;
                padding: 0 !important;
                -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
            }
    
            .paper {
                width: auto !important;
                min-height: auto !important;
                margin: 0 !important;
                padding: 0 !important;
                box-shadow: none !important;
                border: none !important;
                background-color: transparent !important;
            }
    
            .no-print {
                display: none !important;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="paper">
        <div class="header">
            <img class="logo" src="/image/logokebondalem-fix.png" alt="Logo Desa">
            <h3>PEMERINTAH KABUPATEN KLATEN</h3>
            <h3>KECAMATAN PRAMBANAN</h3>
            <h2>DESA&nbsp;KEBONDALEM&nbsp;KIDUL</h2>
            <p>Sekretariat : Bero RT 002 RW 006, Kebondalem Kidul, Prambanan, Klaten. Pos 57454</p>
            <div class="garis-bawah"></div>
            <p class="kode-desa">No. Kode Desa/Kelurahan: 3310.012005</p>
        </div>

        <div class="judul-surat">
            <h3 style="font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; ">SURAT KETERANGAN BEDA IDENTITAS</h3>
            <p style="font-weight: bold; margin-top: -5px;">Nomor : 474 /&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;/ 05 / XI / 2024</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p>Yang bertanda tangan di bawah ini, Kepala Desa Kebondalem Kidul, Kecamatan Prambanan, Kabupaten Klaten, menerangkan bahwa:</p>
            
            <!-- First name field with proper alignment -->
            <div class="first-name-container">
                <p class="first-name-label">Nama</p>
                <p class="first-name-value">: <strong><%= suratKBI.nama ? suratKBI.nama.toUpperCase() : '' %></strong></p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Other data fields with consistent alignment -->
            <div class="data-container">
                <p class="data-label">Yang Tertera di</p>
                <p class="data-value">: <%= suratKBI.tertera || '' %></p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="data-container">
                <p class="data-label">No. Rekening</p>
                <p class="data-value">: <%= suratKBI.norek || '' %></p>
            </div>
            
            <p style="margin-left: 38px;">Dan:</p>
            
            <div class="data-container">
                <p class="data-label">Nama</p>
                <p class="data-value">: <strong><%= suratKBI.nama_lagi ? suratKBI.nama_lagi.toUpperCase() : '' %></strong></p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="data-container">
                <p class="data-label">Yang Tertera di</p>
                <p class="data-value">: <%= suratKBI.tertera_lagi || '' %></p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="data-container">
                <p class="data-label">Nomor Kartu Keluarga</p>
                <p class="data-value">: <%= suratKBI.no_kk || '' %></p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="data-container">
                <p class="data-label">Nomor Induk Kependudukan</p>
                <p class="data-value">: <%= suratKBI.nik || '' %></p>
            </div>
        
            <p style="margin-top: 20px;"><strong>Adalah nama dan data satu orang yang sama.</strong> Adapun surat keterangan ini dibuat sebagai <%= suratKBI.keperluan_surat || 'keperluan lain' %>.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 10px;">Demikian surat keterangan ini dibuat dengan sebenarnya, semoga menjadikan periksa dan dapat dipergunakan sebagaimana mestinya.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="signature-block">
            <div class="signature-container">
                <div class="ttd-kanan">
                    <p class="tanggal-ttd">Kebondalem Kidul, <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString('id-ID', { day: 'numeric', month: 'long', year: 'numeric' }) %></p>
                    <p>a.n Kepala Desa Kebondalem Kidul</p>
                    <p>Sekretaris Desa</p>
                    <div style="height: 60px;"></div>
                    <p class="signature-name">DARU PURNOMO</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="no-print" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
            <button class="btn-print" onclick="window.print()">
                <i class="fas fa-print"></i> Cetak
            </button>
            <button class="btn-back" onclick="window.history.back()">
                <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Kembali
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>